name: Personalis nullus
description:
After washing their feet

one denied three times and stood outside the door

the other sat alone on his throne and held his head

the third was hanging on a tree and no one came to him

she touched the lifeless body and washed it with her hair

Rooster crowed

The sun was shining, but the clouds were above the ground and washed everything with rain

Some people hid in caves and waited for the appearance of a divine child

Personal nobody
Sailors series
